# Azure Virtual Machines Lab

## Objective
Deploy and configure Azure Virtual Machines.

## Environment

### VM01
- Windows 10 Enterprise 22H2
- Standard D4s v3
- South Africa North
- Availability Zone enabled
- Managed Disk (Standard SSD)
- RDP Enabled

### VM02
- Windows 10 Enterprise 22H2
- Standard D4s v3
- Central India
- Availability Zone enabled
- Managed Disk (Standard SSD)
- Accelerated Networking Enabled

## Tasks Completed
- Created two Azure VMs
- Configured networking
- Created public IP addresses
- Configured RDP access
- Applied resource tags
- Added data disks

## Skills Learned
- VM deployment
- Availability Zones
- VM sizing
- Disk management
- Network configuration

